DescPort: <<
Account for Mac OS X's mkdir failing when there's a trailing slash.

Had to add F77=no to configure to get around a weird libtool thing
when "fort77" is installed.

Include popt.h in gnome-gconf.c to allow compilation with GCC 4, see http://cvs.gnome.org/viewcvs/libgnome/libgnome/gnome-gconf.c?r1=1.48&r2=1.49 and http://bugs.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=302071 .
<<
